                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
                           <p>A large stele (<height unit="metre">1.46</height> x <width unit="metre">0.87</width> x <depth unit="metre">0.28</depth>) with a central panel, within simple moulding, topped by a decorated pediment and acroteria and flanked by scrolls. The panel is supported by two winged <rs type="decoration">victories</rs>, holding palms; between them is a smaller figure, with a wheel, identified by Robert as <rs type="decoration">Nemesis</rs>.</p>
                        </support>
